{"type": "article", "id": 9506, "title": "Penxo 铅笔", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-13T07:37:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606002925nmjVtOgXB5RfWZY8.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这是一款没有弹簧，按键等任何机械零件的铅笔，利用古老的重力学控制铅芯的进出。设计师 Brian Ton Tak 试图去除掉铅笔里面复杂的零件，保留最重要的部分。同时，设计师要求它满足可持续发展的需求。因此，这款铅笔使用的材料是航空级的铝 6061-T651 ，材质轻盈并且可以回收使用。目前铅笔外壳有黑色，银色和金色三种颜色可选，售价 35 美元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/bitsfactory/penxo-the-most-minimalistic-2mm-lead-holder-pencil\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002921Xhi9LBN3bCf8140u.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.65036675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002921VcPYU0tIxCEwJDdg.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.40342298\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002922pgiuqVOJN8jA0hFK.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.87163814\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002922lLJjmr7FbCS5E1WP.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002923RckL7zxpvsUl6MZF.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.93857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002924IxUrndEMBKem3ktP.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.00428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002924mo8jPDZwv9CXYQHW.jp